## [function __rating_scale.on_mouse_click__(pos)](#function-__rating_scaleon_mouse_click__pos) {#function-__rating_scaleon_mouse_click__pos}

Is called whenever the user clicks on the widget. Selects the correct value from the scale and optionally closes the form.

__Arguments:__

- `pos` -- An (x, y) coordinates tuple.
	- Type: tuple

</div>

